## Proposed System Architecture

To make Prism excel at website construction, we will tie together four existing and new components within the Prism runtime:

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Operator Request] --> B[Task Decomposer]
    B -->|Decomposes goal| C[Skills Engine]
    C -->|Invokes web-creator skill| D[Main Hemisphere: Coordination]
    D -->|Prompts| E[Spectrum Refraction Triad]
    E -->|Left: Logic & Lint| F[Prism IDE Sandboxed Editor]
    E -->|Right: Creative Assets & CSS| F
    F -->|Executes Code Writes| G[Workspace /prism_public]
    G -->|Runs Audits| H[Browser Control Tool]
    H -->|Playwright Screenshots| I[Visual Consensus Gate]
    I -->|Failed: Retries with error logs| F
    I -->|Passed: Deploys| J[Operator Live Preview]
```

